title: Induction and an epidural were absolutely the right choice for me
text:
by Kelly Wilbanks posted in Pregnancy I sat down in a quiet house to a dinner of steak and lobster--my "last meal" before becoming a mother of three. My induction was scheduled for midnight and I was enjoying the calm before the storm. My two daughters were with Grandma and my husband was finishing his last night... Read more Â»
